TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT vrap.snap_id_seq.nextval ,s.MAX_SNAP_SEQ_NB ,s.MODEL_TYP_CD , s.period_id ,s.RUN_MODE_CD ,(decode(s.max_snap_seq_nb,-1,0,s.MAX_SNAP_SEQ_NB) + 1 ) next_snap_seq_nb ,s.corp_cd FROM (SELECT period_id ,corp_cd ,model_typ_cd ,run_mode_cd ,max(snap_seq_nb) max_snap_seq_nb FROM vrap.tsnap WHERE RUN_MODE_CD = 0 GROUP BY period_id ,corp_cd ,model_typ_cd ,run_mode_cd) s ,vrap.tsnap_rvw_lock l WHERE s.PERIOD_ID = l.PERIOD_ID AND s.MODEL_TYP_CD = l.MODEL_TYP_CD AND l.PRCS_LOCK_CD = 0 -- only open periods --ORDER BY -- substr(s.period_id,1,1) -- ,substr(s.period_id,4,2) -- ,substr(s.period_id,2,2) -- ,s.model_typ_cd -- ,s.run_mode_cd WITH UR
